Package: icinga
Version: 0.8.2
Revision: 2
Depends: gd2-shlibs (>= 2.0.35-4), libiconv (>= 1.12-3), libjpeg-shlibs (>= 6b-17), libpng3-shlibs (>= 1:1.2.35-2), libtool2-shlibs (>= 2.2.6-3)
BuildDepends: gd2 (>= 2.0.35-4), libiconv-dev (>= 1.12-3), libjpeg (>= 6b-17), libpng3 (>= 1:1.2.35-2), libtool2 (>= 2.2.6-3)
Source: mirror:sourceforge:project/%n/%n/%v/%n-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: c29868f2837c32c56426274ae92b5eac
SetLDFLAGS: -I%p/include -L%p/lib
SetCFLAGS: -Os
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man --with-extra-includes=%p/include --with-extra-libs=%p/lib --disable-dependency-tracking --with-httpd-conf=%p/etc/apache2
CompileScript: ./configure %c && grep -rl -- "-o icinga -g icinga" * |xargs perl -pi -e "s,-o icinga -g icinga,,g" && make all
InstallScript: make install DESTDIR=%d && rmdir %i/libexec
DocFiles: AUTHORS LICENSE:COPYING ChangeLog INSTALLING LEGAL README THANKS UPGRADING
License: GPL
Homepage: http://icinga.sourceforge.net
Maintainer: Jack Fink <jackfink@users.sourceforge.net>
Description: Open Source Monitoring System based on Nagios
DescDetail: <<
	Icinga is an Open Source Monitoring System based on Nagios. Icinga will be fully
	compatible with its predecessor, retaining all the existing Nagios features while
	adding new features requested by the user community.
<<
